  "texts": [
    "The authors find that asking the model questions that are posted on a KG representation considerably enhanced the accuracy of the response.",
    "We build on this concept, and the potential that KGs offer for modeling educational content, to support an LLM-based chatbot in generating more relevant explanations for a learning recommendation.",
    "Our contributions in this paper can be summarized in three points: 1) we propose an approach for using chatbots in recommendation explainability tasks.",
    "We use the term \"conversational explainability\" in this paper and define it as the explainability process that takes place through a bi-directional, multi-step interaction between a user and the system, which happens in a certain use-case and within one context.",
    "We consider this type of explanations a natural extension of the conversations between a student and his/her peers or mentors, and thus utilize it in this educational application."
  ],
